Kenneth Morgan Stancil III was arrested sleeping on a Florida beach early on Tuesday morning . 
  He allegedly shot dead his former work-study supervisor Ron Lane at Wayne County Community College in Goldsboro on Monday morning . 
  Lane had worked at the college for 18 years but was fired with no notice . 
  His mother has claimed that Lane had made unwanted sexual advances towards her son . 
  He was found sleeping on the beach and faces one count of open murder . 
  Police are investigating the shooting as a possible hate crime . 
 